00:03:58.338 --> 00:03:59.540 position:19% line:83% align:start
[announcer] <i>Both teams</i>
 <i>have put forth</i>

00:03:59.574 --> 00:04:01.576 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>their best effort</i>
 <i>to be here.</i>

00:04:01.609 --> 00:04:02.910 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>It's the moment of truth.</i>

00:04:02.944 --> 00:04:04.145 position:19% line:89% align:start
