how important this match is?

00:04:23.296 --> 00:04:25.099 position:24% line:83% align:start
Now more than ever,
we have to--

00:04:25.133 --> 00:04:26.834 position:16% line:83% align:start
[Yayoi] Come on, Tsubasa,
score on them!

