What? What?

00:04:28.002 --> 00:04:31.471 position:16% line:83% align:start
I thought I heard someone
yelling out Tsubasa's name.

00:04:31.506 --> 00:04:33.306 position:21% line:83% align:start
You thought you were
his only fan?

00:04:33.340 --> 00:04:34.876 position:21% line:83% align:start
There's tons of girls
that cheer him.

