 <i>his team leader</i>
 <i>Morimichi Kawakami,</i>

00:05:03.470 --> 00:05:04.806 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>their prodigy.</i>

00:05:04.839 --> 00:05:07.542 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>With a 4-4-2 formation,</i>
 <i>they're a well-rounded team</i>

00:05:07.575 --> 00:05:09.544 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>who doesn't fall short</i>
 <i>to Nankatsu.</i>

00:05:09.577 --> 00:05:11.646 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>Their players</i>
 <i>are very strong.</i>

00:05:11.679 --> 00:05:13.581 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>Both teams have</i>
 <i>practically scored</i>

