 <i>the same amount of goals</i>
 <i>in their matches.</i>

00:05:15.750 --> 00:05:17.685 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>Which makes it hard</i>
 <i>to predict the winner</i>

00:05:17.718 --> 00:05:21.055 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>of this nail-biting</i>
 <i>encounter.</i>

