-[grunt]
-[pants]

00:07:10.264 --> 00:07:11.498 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[scream]
-[announcer] <i>Taro Misaki</i>

00:07:11.532 --> 00:07:13.466 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>receives it and passes</i>
 <i>without thinking twice,</i>

00:07:13.501 --> 00:07:15.636 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>back to Tsubasa whom</i>
 <i>runs towards the goal.</i>

00:07:17.972 --> 00:07:20.041 position:19% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa, you can do it!

00:07:21.742 --> 00:07:22.510 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:07:22.543 --> 00:07:23.778 position:35% line:83% align:start
[announcer]
 <i>And there it is.</i>

00:07:23.811 --> 00:07:26.479 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>Nankatsu's number ten's</i>
 <i>shot is a fierce one.</i>

00:07:26.514 --> 00:07:27.682 position:30% line:83% align:start
- <i>But the ball</i>
-[gasp]

00:07:27.715 --> 00:07:29.650 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>hits the goal post</i>
 <i>with a direct impact.</i>

00:07:29.684 --> 00:07:31.652 position:19% line:83% align:start
Oh! Hey, that should've
gone in.

00:07:31.686 --> 00:07:33.888 position:21% line:83% align:start
-That was too close.
-Too close for comfort.

00:07:35.323 --> 00:07:37.425 position:44% line:83% align:start
Uh...
[growl]

00:07:37.457 --> 00:07:38.592 position:16% line:89% align:start
That wasn't enough guys.

00:07:38.626 --> 00:07:40.294 position:10% line:83% align:start
[Morimichi] We need one more
to cover him.

00:07:40.328 --> 00:07:42.563 position:16% line:83% align:start
Aww, that shot should've
made it in.

00:07:42.596 --> 00:07:43.731 position:27% line:89% align:start
That's not fair.

00:07:43.764 --> 00:07:45.433 position:10% line:83% align:start
-[Yayoi] It's okay, Tsubasa.
-Huh?

00:07:45.465 --> 00:07:46.701 position:21% line:89% align:start
Don't worry about it.

00:07:46.734 --> 00:07:48.569 position:13% line:83% align:start
You'll get to score a goal
next time.

00:07:48.602 --> 00:07:51.372 position:16% line:83% align:start
[gasp] Who does she think
she is?

00:07:51.405 --> 00:07:53.607 position:44% line:83% align:start
Huh?
Hey, Sanae, wait up!

00:07:53.641 --> 00:07:55.509 position:27% line:83% align:start
-[Yayoi] Tsubasa!
-Huh?

00:07:55.543 --> 00:07:56.844 position:16% line:89% align:start
Did you forget about me?

00:07:56.877 --> 00:07:58.913 position:30% line:89% align:start
It's me! Yayoi!

00:07:58.946 --> 00:08:00.815 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Yayoi]
I came to cheer you on.

00:08:01.916 --> 00:08:02.717 position:38% line:89% align:start
[chuckle]

00:08:02.750 --> 00:08:03.584 position:44% line:89% align:start
Uh...

00:08:03.617 --> 00:08:05.485 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[laughs]
-[laughs]

00:08:05.519 --> 00:08:06.787 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Sanae]
Hey, just wait a second!

00:08:06.821 --> 00:08:08.055 position:38% line:89% align:start
Oh! Huh?

00:08:08.089 --> 00:08:09.924 position:10% line:89% align:start
What's with you and Tsubasa?

00:08:09.957 --> 00:08:10.791 position:33% line:89% align:start
Who are you?

00:08:10.825 --> 00:08:13.527 position:13% line:89% align:start
Hello and who might you be?

00:08:13.561 --> 00:08:15.730 position:27% line:83% align:start
I'm the leader of
Nankatsu's cheering squad.

00:08:15.763 --> 00:08:18.466 position:24% line:83% align:start
And I also protect
Tsubasa from harpies.

00:08:18.498 --> 00:08:19.667 position:30% line:89% align:start
I can see that.

00:08:19.700 --> 00:08:21.736 position:21% line:83% align:start
Tsubasa and I used to
go to the same school.

00:08:21.769 --> 00:08:23.537 position:19% line:89% align:start
My name is Yayoi Aoba.

00:08:23.571 --> 00:08:24.972 position:27% line:89% align:start
Nice to meet you.

00:08:25.006 --> 00:08:26.507 position:16% line:89% align:start
Hey, cutie, how are you?

00:08:26.540 --> 00:08:27.908 position:19% line:83% align:start
-I'm also a-- [scream]
-[grunt]

00:08:27.942 --> 00:08:30.578 position:24% line:83% align:start
You shut up, Koji.
Don't be a bootlicker.

00:08:30.611 --> 00:08:33.614 position:21% line:83% align:start
Tsubasa is incredible
when he plays, isn't he?

00:08:33.647 --> 00:08:35.282 position:16% line:83% align:start
-He's got so much energy.
-[groan]

00:08:35.316 --> 00:08:36.917 position:35% line:89% align:start
Ah... Huh?

00:08:38.819 --> 00:08:40.621 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Yayoi] I remember him
playing with his soccer ball

00:08:40.654 --> 00:08:42.089 position:19% line:89% align:start
at school all day long.

00:08:42.123 --> 00:08:43.491 position:16% line:89% align:start
He was never without it.

00:08:43.524 --> 00:08:45.026 position:19% line:83% align:start
While watching him play
in the field,

00:08:45.059 --> 00:08:47.595 position:30% line:83% align:start
I can tell that
his heart really...

00:08:47.628 --> 00:08:49.497 position:21% line:89% align:start
belongs to the field.

00:08:49.530 --> 00:08:51.098 position:16% line:89% align:start
He looks so much happier.

00:08:52.199 --> 00:08:54.668 position:13% line:83% align:start
Back then, everyone thought
that he was weird...

00:08:54.702 --> 00:08:56.737 position:16% line:83% align:start
because he spent his days
playing soccer.

00:08:56.771 --> 00:08:59.740 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>Doesn't he ever get tired</i>
 <i>of playing with the ball?</i>

00:08:59.774 --> 00:09:01.510 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Yayoi]
But I was fascinated with

00:09:01.542 --> 00:09:03.210 position:27% line:83% align:start
Tsubasa's passion
for soccer.

00:09:03.244 --> 00:09:04.078 position:24% line:89% align:start
He never got tired.

00:09:04.111 --> 00:09:07.448 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>Yayoi, we want to</i>
 <i>leave already.</i>

00:09:07.481 --> 00:09:09.583 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[growl]
-It was sad.

00:09:09.617 --> 00:09:11.886 position:19% line:83% align:start
I never could tell him
how I felt for him.

00:09:11.919 --> 00:09:13.354 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Yayoi]
By the time I realized,

00:09:13.387 --> 00:09:14.588 position:21% line:89% align:start
he had already left.

00:09:15.056 --> 00:09:15.856 position:41% line:89% align:start
[growl]

00:09:15.890 --> 00:09:17.591 position:24% line:83% align:start
Aren't you going to
cheer for him?

00:09:17.625 --> 00:09:19.794 position:16% line:83% align:start
Tsubasa has the ball now
and he's running.

00:09:19.827 --> 00:09:20.661 position:41% line:89% align:start
What?!

00:09:20.694 --> 00:09:22.029 position:35% line:83% align:start
[announcer]
 <i>The ball lands directly</i>

00:09:22.063 --> 00:09:23.564 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>on Tsubasa's chest.</i>

00:09:23.597 --> 00:09:24.832 position:41% line:83% align:start
[grunt]
Huh?

00:09:24.865 --> 00:09:25.900 position:35% line:83% align:start
[announcer]
 <i>But now there are</i>

00:09:25.933 --> 00:09:28.503 position:21% line:83% align:start
three Shimizu players
covering him.

00:09:28.537 --> 00:09:29.904 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa]
 <i>Now, there's three players?</i>

00:09:29.937 --> 00:09:30.671 position:38% line:89% align:start
[snicker]

00:09:30.704 --> 00:09:32.273 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Suzuki]
You want three on him?

00:09:32.306 --> 00:09:33.441 position:33% line:89% align:start
Yes, exactly.

00:09:33.474 --> 00:09:35.643 position:13% line:83% align:start
But if we were to do that,
wouldn't our goal

00:09:35.676 --> 00:09:37.512 position:19% line:83% align:start
be totally defenseless,
Captain?

00:09:37.546 --> 00:09:38.746 position:21% line:89% align:start
You're overreacting.

00:09:38.779 --> 00:09:40.815 position:10% line:89% align:start
Even if he dares to shoot...

00:09:40.848 --> 00:09:43.417 position:19% line:83% align:start
I know that I can stop
his shot easily.

00:09:43.451 --> 00:09:44.351 position:24% line:89% align:start
That's my job here.

00:09:45.453 --> 00:09:47.888 position:21% line:83% align:start
He's the only scorer
Nankatsu's got.

00:09:47.922 --> 00:09:50.925 position:19% line:83% align:start
Which means if we cover
Tsubasa the whole time...

00:09:50.958 --> 00:09:53.194 position:19% line:83% align:start
there's no way they can
score on us.

00:09:54.095 --> 00:09:55.429 position:35% line:83% align:start
[announcer]
 <i>This is the first time</i>

00:09:55.463 --> 00:09:58.599 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>Tsubasa's being covered</i>
 <i>by three players at a time.</i>

00:09:58.632 --> 00:10:00.101 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>How will he overcome</i>
 <i>this strategy</i>

00:10:00.134 --> 00:10:01.503 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>by Team Shimizu?</i>

00:10:01.536 --> 00:10:02.837 position:35% line:83% align:start
 <i>There are</i>
 <i>no teammates near him.</i>

00:10:02.870 --> 00:10:04.472 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Roberto]
 <i>What will you do, Tsubasa?</i>

00:10:04.506 --> 00:10:05.606 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>The more they know you,</i>

00:10:05.639 --> 00:10:07.174 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>the more pressure</i>
 <i>the opposing team</i>

00:10:07.208 --> 00:10:08.042 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>will put on you.</i>

00:10:08.075 --> 00:10:10.144 position:19% line:83% align:start
-Tsubasa! Pass it here!
-Huh?

00:10:10.177 --> 00:10:11.846 position:30% line:83% align:start
-[grunt] Here!
-No!

00:10:11.879 --> 00:10:12.746 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:10:12.780 --> 00:10:14.248 position:21% line:83% align:start
If you keep covering
Tsubasa like that,

00:10:14.281 --> 00:10:16.150 position:21% line:83% align:start
you're giving us all
the freedom in the world.

00:10:16.183 --> 00:10:16.750 position:41% line:89% align:start
Teppei!

00:10:16.784 --> 00:10:17.885 position:41% line:83% align:start
[grunt]
I got it!

00:10:17.918 --> 00:10:18.819 position:35% line:83% align:start
[announcer]
 <i>The Nankatsu Team</i>

00:10:18.853 --> 00:10:19.920 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>passes the ball freely.</i>

00:10:19.954 --> 00:10:21.989 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>Teppei Kisugi exploits</i>
 <i>the weak defense</i>

00:10:22.022 --> 00:10:24.725 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>and manages to make</i>
 <i>his way to the penalty area.</i>

00:10:24.758 --> 00:10:26.861 position:35% line:83% align:start
 <i>He sets up</i>
 <i>his shot and...</i>

00:10:27.795 --> 00:10:29.864 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>Morimichi Kawakami</i>
 <i>stops it!</i>

00:10:29.897 --> 00:10:32.633 position:41% line:83% align:start
-What?
-What a nice catch, Captain!

00:10:33.535 --> 00:10:34.768 position:35% line:83% align:start
[announcer]
 <i>What a great catch</i>

00:10:34.802 --> 00:10:37.838 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>made by the star player</i>
 <i>of Shimizu.</i>

00:10:37.872 --> 00:10:40.307 position:24% line:83% align:start
Nankatsu might have
Genzo on their side,

00:10:40.341 --> 00:10:43.545 position:19% line:83% align:start
but Team Shimizu has me
in covering their goal.

00:10:43.578 --> 00:10:45.646 position:35% line:89% align:start
[cheering]

00:10:45.679 --> 00:10:49.116 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>Morimichi is</i>
 <i>a very good goalkeeper.</i>

00:10:49.150 --> 00:10:50.751 position:38% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa!

00:10:50.784 --> 00:10:52.253 position:13% line:89% align:start
Have it your way, groupie.

00:10:52.286 --> 00:10:55.156 position:19% line:83% align:start
We'll settle this once
the match is over.

00:10:55.189 --> 00:10:56.558 position:21% line:89% align:start
Everyone, go forward!

00:10:56.591 --> 00:10:57.791 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:11:00.194 --> 00:11:02.863 position:24% line:83% align:start
[announcer] <i>This is</i>
 <i>going to be a fierce battle.</i>

00:11:02.897 --> 00:11:04.665 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>They are very even.</i>

00:11:04.698 --> 00:11:05.799 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>It looks like</i>
 <i>neither team</i>

00:11:05.833 --> 00:11:08.102 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>wants to give up ground</i>
 <i>on the pitch.</i>

00:11:08.135 --> 00:11:09.638 position:24% line:89% align:start
Uh... Here it goes!

00:11:09.670 --> 00:11:11.705 position:16% line:83% align:start
[announcer] <i>Team Shimizu</i>
 <i>fires up a shot</i>

00:11:11.739 --> 00:11:13.007 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>towards Nankatsu's goal.</i>

00:11:14.108 --> 00:11:16.645 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>But the genius goalkeeper</i>
 <i>Genzo Wakabayashi</i>

00:11:16.677 --> 00:11:18.179 position:16% line:83% align:start
- <i>easily stops that shot.</i>
-[grunt]

00:11:18.212 --> 00:11:19.648 position:35% line:83% align:start
-[chuckle]
-[announcer] <i>Looks like</i>

00:11:19.680 --> 00:11:21.650 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>Nankatsu's goalkeeper</i>
 <i>is in perfect condition</i>

00:11:21.682 --> 00:11:23.083 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>to defend the team's goal.</i>

00:11:23.117 --> 00:11:24.385 position:24% line:83% align:start
- <i>No injuries here.</i>
-[whistle]

00:11:24.418 --> 00:11:26.655 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>The referee whistles</i>
 <i>the end of the first half.</i>

00:11:26.687 --> 00:11:27.855 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>We'll go on break</i>

00:11:27.888 --> 00:11:30.024 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>with both teams tied up</i>
 <i>on the scoreboard.</i>

00:11:32.059 --> 00:11:33.662 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Genzo]
 <i>While I'm standing here,</i>

00:11:33.694 --> 00:11:35.896 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>there'll be no goals</i>
 <i>for Shimizu.</i>

00:11:36.797 --> 00:11:38.832 position:35% line:83% align:start
[Morimichi]
 <i>Don't get too cocky now.</i>

00:11:38.866 --> 00:11:41.802 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>Or you'll end up</i>
 <i>regretting it, Genzo.</i>

00:11:41.835 --> 00:11:43.370 position:35% line:83% align:start
[narrator]
 <i>We'll be back with</i>

00:11:48.375 --> 00:11:49.476 position:35% line:83% align:start
[narrator]
 <i>And we're back!</i>

00:11:51.745 --> 00:11:55.449 position:38% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:11:55.482 --> 00:11:56.618 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sigh]

00:11:56.651 --> 00:11:58.385 position:35% line:83% align:start
Those guys
from Shimizu are strong.

00:11:58.419 --> 00:12:01.021 position:13% line:83% align:start
That's true. I had no idea
they were that good.

00:12:01.055 --> 00:12:03.257 position:24% line:83% align:start
Winning this match
won't be easy.

00:12:03.290 --> 00:12:04.258 position:33% line:89% align:start
We know that.

00:12:04.291 --> 00:12:05.694 position:21% line:89% align:start
Everybody, calm down!

00:12:05.726 --> 00:12:07.161 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-Listen up!

00:12:07.194 --> 00:12:08.762 position:27% line:83% align:start
All we have to do
during this match

00:12:08.796 --> 00:12:10.532 position:21% line:89% align:start
is to score one goal.

00:12:10.565 --> 00:12:11.832 position:16% line:89% align:start
But keep this in mind...

00:12:11.865 --> 00:12:14.603 position:13% line:83% align:start
they'll be covering Tsubasa
all the time.

00:12:14.636 --> 00:12:15.970 position:19% line:83% align:start
So don't forget to play
as a team

00:12:16.003 --> 00:12:17.539 position:19% line:89% align:start
throughout this match.

00:12:17.572 --> 00:12:18.472 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Yes!
-Yes!

00:12:18.506 --> 00:12:19.641 position:10% line:89% align:start
We didn't come here to lose.

00:12:19.674 --> 00:12:20.841 position:13% line:89% align:start
We came to defeat Shimizu.

00:12:20.874 --> 00:12:21.909 position:38% line:83% align:start
-Exactly.
-Exactly.

00:12:21.942 --> 00:12:24.211 position:33% line:83% align:start
We will go to
the national tournament.

00:12:24.245 --> 00:12:25.012 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yeah!

00:12:25.045 --> 00:12:26.480 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Teppei]
Let's win this, team!

00:12:26.514 --> 00:12:27.515 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Yes!
-Yes!

00:12:29.049 --> 00:12:31.418 position:19% line:83% align:start
Hey, guys, I'm going to
score that goal for you.

00:12:31.452 --> 00:12:32.119 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:12:32.721 --> 00:12:34.188 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Genzo]
Tsubasa...

00:12:34.221 --> 00:12:36.625 position:33% line:83% align:start
In that case,
we will be counting on you.

00:12:36.658 --> 00:12:37.825 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yes!

00:12:39.927 --> 00:12:40.961 position:19% line:89% align:start
During the second half,

00:12:40.995 --> 00:12:43.397 position:24% line:83% align:start
I want you to cover
Tsubasa better.

00:12:43.430 --> 00:12:44.398 position:16% line:89% align:start
We need to win by a goal

00:12:44.431 --> 00:12:45.299 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>Captain Tsubasa!</i>

00:12:45.332 --> 00:12:47.034 position:27% line:83% align:start
or we won't go to
the national tournament.

00:12:47.067 --> 00:12:48.202 position:13% line:89% align:start
So from this point onward,

00:12:48.235 --> 00:12:50.337 position:33% line:83% align:start
our strategy
will go as follows.

00:12:51.338 --> 00:12:52.607 position:41% line:83% align:start
[coach]
We'll destroy their goalie,

00:12:52.641 --> 00:12:53.073 position:24% line:89% align:start
Genzo Wakabayashi!

00:12:54.174 --> 00:12:56.343 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Morimichi] If we stop
Tsubasa's offensive plays,

00:12:56.377 --> 00:12:59.079 position:27% line:83% align:start
and we neutralize
Genzo's defensive skills,

00:12:59.113 --> 00:13:00.548 position:33% line:83% align:start
victory will
fall on our laps

00:13:00.582 --> 00:13:02.016 position:19% line:89% align:start
without a doubt, Coach.

00:13:02.049 --> 00:13:04.118 position:21% line:83% align:start
I have a feeling that
their goalkeepers' injury

00:13:04.151 --> 00:13:06.521 position:24% line:83% align:start
isn't fully healed
quite yet.

00:13:06.554 --> 00:13:07.855 position:27% line:89% align:start
Listen up, guys,

00:13:07.888 --> 00:13:10.592 position:16% line:83% align:start
we'll be the ones playing
at the national tournament.

00:13:10.625 --> 00:13:11.825 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Yeah!
-Yeah!

00:13:12.826 --> 00:13:15.396 position:19% line:83% align:start
-That was a good game.
-Yeah!

00:13:15.429 --> 00:13:16.631 position:13% line:89% align:start
I've been thinking it over.

00:13:16.665 --> 00:13:17.632 position:33% line:83% align:start
I'm going to
talk to that girl

00:13:17.666 --> 00:13:18.866 position:24% line:89% align:start
right this instant.

00:13:19.967 --> 00:13:22.136 position:24% line:83% align:start
She's an angel that
fell from the heavens...

00:13:22.169 --> 00:13:23.571 position:16% line:83% align:start
a flower that beautifies
