00:18:36.918 --> 00:18:38.218 position:35% line:83% align:start
[announcer]
 <i>What a goal!</i>

00:18:38.251 --> 00:18:40.755 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>Team Nankatsu is now</i>
 <i>up by two goals to nothing.</i>

00:18:40.788 --> 00:18:41.623 position:38% line:89% align:start
[laughs]

00:18:41.656 --> 00:18:42.890 position:35% line:83% align:start
[announcer]
 <i>After the first goal,</i>

00:18:42.924 --> 00:18:46.094 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>Team Nankatsu's been</i>
 <i>revitalized.</i>

00:18:46.126 --> 00:18:48.596 position:38% line:83% align:start
[laughs]
Tsubasa's incredible.

00:18:48.630 --> 00:18:51.599 position:16% line:83% align:start
Tell me, don't you think
he's fantastic?

00:18:51.633 --> 00:18:52.366 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yeah.

00:18:53.333 --> 00:18:55.570 position:27% line:83% align:start
I'm happy we came
all the way to Shizuoka

00:18:55.603 --> 00:18:56.571 position:35% line:89% align:start
to see him.

00:18:58.940 --> 00:19:01.776 position:21% line:83% align:start
[narrator] <i>Musashino</i>
 <i>Elementary School, Tokyo.</i>

00:19:01.809 --> 00:19:02.710 position:21% line:89% align:start
Yeah, you can do it!

00:19:02.744 --> 00:19:04.378 position:19% line:83% align:start
-Over here! Over here!
-Pass it, pass it!

00:19:04.411 --> 00:19:05.980 position:16% line:89% align:start
Hey, let's move already!

00:19:06.014 --> 00:19:07.682 position:13% line:89% align:start
Ugh, what a waste of time.

00:19:07.715 --> 00:19:08.883 position:30% line:89% align:start
He isn't here.

00:19:08.916 --> 00:19:10.317 position:21% line:89% align:start
Hey, Kojiro, tell me,

00:19:10.350 --> 00:19:12.386 position:24% line:83% align:start
who did we come see
at this school?

00:19:12.419 --> 00:19:14.388 position:21% line:83% align:start
I wanted to come see
two players...

00:19:14.421 --> 00:19:17.457 position:21% line:83% align:start
just before we played
our next match.

00:19:17.491 --> 00:19:19.894 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Kojiro] One of them is
Genzo Wakabayashi,

00:19:19.927 --> 00:19:21.428 position:30% line:89% align:start
from Nankatsu.

00:19:21.461 --> 00:19:22.797 position:13% line:89% align:start
And the other player is...

00:19:22.830 --> 00:19:26.333 position:13% line:83% align:start
Jun Misugi from Musashi FC,
a high profile player.

00:19:26.366 --> 00:19:28.368 position:13% line:83% align:start
But neither of them is here
right now.

00:19:28.402 --> 00:19:30.337 position:16% line:89% align:start
I don't know Jun Misugi.

00:19:30.370 --> 00:19:32.406 position:21% line:89% align:start
You serious, Takeshi?

00:19:32.439 --> 00:19:34.408 position:33% line:83% align:start
They call him
the Prince of the Pitch.

00:19:34.441 --> 00:19:36.577 position:30% line:83% align:start
A very talented
young player.

00:19:36.611 --> 00:19:37.912 position:30% line:89% align:start
You can do it!

00:19:39.047 --> 00:19:40.280 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:19:40.313 --> 00:19:41.582 position:16% line:83% align:start
[announcer] <i>And the ball</i>
 <i>is in the clutches of</i>

00:19:41.616 --> 00:19:44.251 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>Nankatsu's goalkeeper,</i>
 <i>Genzo Wakabayashi.</i>

00:19:44.284 --> 00:19:45.385 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>Despite his injury,</i>

00:19:45.419 --> 00:19:46.854 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>Genzo is risking</i>
 <i>everything</i>

00:19:46.888 --> 00:19:48.255 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>to defend his goal.</i>

00:19:48.288 --> 00:19:49.456 position:38% line:83% align:start
 <i>Nankatsu</i>
 <i>can taste victory</i>

00:19:49.489 --> 00:19:51.059 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>at the tip of</i>
 <i>their tongue.</i>

00:19:51.092 --> 00:19:52.459 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>There's only one minute</i>
 <i>on the clock.</i>

00:19:52.492 --> 00:19:54.896 position:21% line:83% align:start
Listen up, I want you
to give me another goal.

00:19:54.929 --> 00:19:55.630 position:38% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa!

00:19:56.731 --> 00:19:58.866 position:27% line:83% align:start
[announcer] <i>Genzo</i>
 <i>passes the ball to Tsubasa,</i>

00:19:58.900 --> 00:20:01.435 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>the star striker</i>
 <i>of Nankatsu.</i>

00:20:01.468 --> 00:20:02.970 position:38% line:83% align:start
Stop him.
Don't let him shoot.

00:20:05.073 --> 00:20:07.474 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa] <i>I know where</i>
 <i>I need to shoot.</i>

00:20:07.508 --> 00:20:08.609 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:20:12.279 --> 00:20:13.514 position:35% line:83% align:start
[announcer]
 <i>Great goal!</i>

00:20:13.548 --> 00:20:15.683 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>Tsubasa gets a hat trick!</i>

00:20:15.717 --> 00:20:17.250 position:38% line:89% align:start
[whistle]

00:20:17.284 --> 00:20:19.187 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>The referee signals</i>
 <i>the end of the match.</i>

00:20:19.252 --> 00:20:23.024 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>Team Nankatsu is</i>
 <i>the champion of Shizuoka!</i>

00:20:23.057 --> 00:20:24.324 position:24% line:89% align:start
Yeah, that's right!

00:20:24.357 --> 00:20:25.526 position:21% line:83% align:start
[announcer] <i>The team</i>
 <i>that is going to represent</i>

00:20:25.560 --> 00:20:27.929 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>our prefecture at</i>
 <i>the national tournament</i>

00:20:27.962 --> 00:20:29.296 position:38% line:83% align:start
- <i>will be</i>
-I'm so happy right now!

00:20:29.329 --> 00:20:30.598 position:21% line:83% align:start
- <i>the Nankatsu squad.</i>
-Me too.

00:20:30.631 --> 00:20:31.364 position:35% line:89% align:start
 <i>Until now,</i>

00:20:31.398 --> 00:20:33.266 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>Tsubasa has made</i>
 <i>three goals</i>

00:20:33.300 --> 00:20:35.402 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>in every single match.</i>

00:20:35.435 --> 00:20:37.839 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>He's a talent</i>
 <i>we've never seen before.</i>

00:20:37.872 --> 00:20:39.207 position:33% line:89% align:start
 <i>Incredible.</i>

00:20:39.239 --> 00:20:40.407 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Genzo]
 <i>You really are incredible.</i>

00:20:40.440 --> 00:20:41.709 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>Job well done, Tsubasa.</i>

00:20:41.743 --> 00:20:43.410 position:13% line:83% align:start
-Good job out there, guys!
-Great work, team!

00:20:43.443 --> 00:20:45.312 position:13% line:89% align:start
What a pity, they beat us.

00:20:45.345 --> 00:20:47.982 position:13% line:83% align:start
We couldn't defeat Tsubasa
or Genzo Wakabayashi.

00:20:48.015 --> 00:20:49.083 position:30% line:89% align:start
They're better.

00:20:49.117 --> 00:20:50.551 position:19% line:89% align:start
Yeah, tell us about it.

00:20:50.585 --> 00:20:52.419 position:24% line:83% align:start
We couldn't compete
on their level.

00:20:52.452 --> 00:20:53.821 position:16% line:89% align:start
They won fair and square.

00:20:55.123 --> 00:20:57.024 position:13% line:89% align:start
It was a good match, guys.

00:20:57.058 --> 00:20:58.726 position:33% line:89% align:start
Oh! Tsubasa!

00:20:58.760 --> 00:20:59.259 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:21:00.094 --> 00:21:01.495 position:24% line:83% align:start
Go to the national
tournament...

00:21:01.529 --> 00:21:03.497 position:24% line:83% align:start
and you win it for
all of us, you got that?

00:21:03.531 --> 00:21:06.466 position:38% line:83% align:start
[laughs]
Thank you, Morimichi.

00:21:06.500 --> 00:21:07.367 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yeah!

00:21:07.400 --> 00:21:08.503 position:24% line:89% align:start
They really did it.

00:21:08.536 --> 00:21:09.570 position:19% line:89% align:start
Everything ended well.

00:21:09.604 --> 00:21:10.437 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yes.

00:21:10.470 --> 00:21:11.739 position:30% line:83% align:start
-Hey, Tsubasa!
-[Yayoi] Hey, Tsubasa!

00:21:11.773 --> 00:21:14.407 position:21% line:83% align:start
-Congratulations on--
-Congratulations on winning!

00:21:14.441 --> 00:21:15.375 position:21% line:89% align:start
It's that brat again!

00:21:15.408 --> 00:21:16.544 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Yayoi]
You were great!

00:21:16.577 --> 00:21:19.113 position:24% line:83% align:start
I hope I see you at
the national tournament.

00:21:19.147 --> 00:21:20.715 position:19% line:83% align:start
I got transferred too,
you know?

00:21:20.748 --> 00:21:23.184 position:27% line:83% align:start
And now, I'm with
Team Musashi from Tokyo.

00:21:23.217 --> 00:21:25.385 position:13% line:89% align:start
I hope I see you very soon.

00:21:25.418 --> 00:21:27.755 position:44% line:83% align:start
Uh...
I think I know that player.

00:21:27.789 --> 00:21:29.023 position:21% line:89% align:start
You know him, Coach?

00:21:29.056 --> 00:21:30.423 position:24% line:89% align:start
Tell us who he is.

00:21:30.457 --> 00:21:32.160 position:41% line:83% align:start
[coach]
His name's Jun Misugi.

00:21:32.193 --> 00:21:33.961 position:21% line:83% align:start
One of most talented
young players

00:21:33.995 --> 00:21:35.362 position:16% line:89% align:start
in the league right now.

00:21:35.395 --> 00:21:37.464 position:13% line:89% align:start
He's an exceptional player.

00:21:37.497 --> 00:21:39.267 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa]
 <i>Jun Misugi...</i>

00:21:39.299 --> 00:21:40.568 position:19% line:89% align:start
You take care, Tsubasa.

00:21:41.702 --> 00:21:44.404 position:16% line:83% align:start
[Sanae] Who the hell does
she think she is?

00:21:44.437 --> 00:21:45.405 position:27% line:83% align:start
I guess I'll just
have to become

00:21:45.438 --> 00:21:46.974 position:13% line:89% align:start
the team's representative.

00:21:47.008 --> 00:21:48.408 position:21% line:83% align:start
-I'll be the manager.
-Huh?

00:21:48.441 --> 00:21:49.744 position:38% line:83% align:start
That way,
I'll be able to go to

00:21:49.777 --> 00:21:51.411 position:19% line:83% align:start
the national tournament
right next to

00:21:51.444 --> 00:21:53.346 position:21% line:83% align:start
-my handsome Tsubasa.
-Ugh...

00:21:54.182 --> 00:21:55.216 position:35% line:83% align:start
[narrator]
 <i>And so,</i>

00:21:55.249 --> 00:21:56.617 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>the single elimination</i>
 <i>tournament</i>

00:21:56.651 --> 00:21:59.352 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>to choose Shizuoka</i>
 <i>prefecture's team concluded.</i>

00:21:59.386 --> 00:22:00.487 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>Leaving Nankatsu</i>

00:22:00.521 --> 00:22:03.124 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>as the centerpiece</i>
 <i>of all the matches.</i>

00:22:03.157 --> 00:22:05.526 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>In the meantime,</i>
 <i>the Wangan stadium,</i>

00:22:05.560 --> 00:22:06.994 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>where the national</i>
 <i>tournament matches</i>

00:22:07.028 --> 00:22:07.795 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>will be held,</i>

00:22:07.829 --> 00:22:09.964 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>anxiously awaits</i>
 <i>the arrival of</i>

00:22:09.997 --> 00:22:11.766 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>the new young players.</i>

00:22:15.536 --> 00:22:17.437 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Roberto]
You did it, Tsubasa.

00:22:18.306 --> 00:22:19.372 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yeah!

00:22:19.406 --> 00:22:21.509 position:27% line:83% align:start
The next step is
the national tournament.

00:22:21.542 --> 00:22:24.812 position:13% line:83% align:start
From now on, you'll have to
play seriously.

00:22:24.846 --> 00:22:26.113 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa]
Yeah.

00:22:26.147 --> 00:22:27.515 position:21% line:89% align:start
That's how it'll be.

00:22:28.415 --> 00:22:30.151 position:38% line:83% align:start
I'll win
the national tournament,

00:22:30.184 --> 00:22:31.953 position:16% line:83% align:start
and I'll go with Roberto
to Brazil

00:22:31.986 --> 00:22:33.721 position:10% line:89% align:start
to be a professional player.

